**Vlad breaks into the open from the Alliance base and looks around as the 
battle takes place around him, glaring at some bots and scanning their spark 
signatures. None of them turned to be Predacons, which meant that he could 
join in on this battle after all.
He didn't really want to turn on the factor which he was using at the 
moment, but as soon as he spotted a proper Pred unit, he would leave this 
place.
Shesta came up behind Vlad and yipped, eager to try and knock someone down 
while Vlad acted quickly and slit their throat. Like so many turns he had 
done in the past.
As it was, he alwats got what he wanted. And if it was a bots hide, he got 
it!
Vlad looked on and finally decided on just who would be the one he could 
test his skill: Prebon!
He moved a little towards him but knew better then to get too close, 
thinking that he would rather test this robots' abilities first and rate his 
power. To see just what sort of weapons he would need to take him down.
Vlad removed a phaser from his arm, it swinging up and into his palm from 
the underside of his wrist.
With the gun right in place his fingers closed around the handle and another 
squeezed the trigger, aiming towards Prebons shoulder.**
